Various Random Notes====================by Drew DavidsonBrief Notes on World Scaling~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Files:  AppDeflt.[cpp,h]Not sure what this means, but there may be relevant info in DefaultPreferenceand UnitPreference.  DefaultPreference instance variables:	Point3DFFixed	localOrigin;	/* the local origin of the design views */	Point3DFFixed	homePosition;	/* app's default home position	*/UnitPreference instance variables:	short			unitSystem;	/* app's default unit system			*/	double			unitSize;	/* app's default unit system			*/	double			baseSize;	/* app's default base rendering size	*/	double			worldSize;	/* app's default world rendering size	*/	double			customSize;	/* app's default world rendering size	*/Brief Notes on Camera Position~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Files:  Observer.[cpp,h], WlkCntrl.[cpp,h]WalkController *wlkcntrl->observer->GetPosition(Point3DFFixed *pt,Angle3DFFixed *ang)returns current observer position and orientation (preferred method).Observer instance variables:	Point3DFFixed    FFpoint,lastPoint;	Angle3DFFixed    FFangle,lastAngle;	Angle3D          lastAngle256;Brief Notes on Lights~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Files:  Light.[cpp,h]appPref->model->lights contains the light model (appPref is AppPreference*)appPref->model->lights is a LightModel, which is a V_Array with all of the lights  (V_Array of Light objects)if light->Ambient() then light is ambientLight instance variables:	Point3D source;				/* where the light is == {0,0,0} for ambient lights */	RGBColor color;				/* what color it emits */	short brightness;			/* intensity of light source */	short active;				/* is the light shining? */